# CW Node Helper — Setup wizard demo
# Record: vhs assets/tapes/setup.tape
Output assets/setup.gif
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set FontSize 14
Set FontFamily "SF Mono"
Set Theme "Builtin Dark"
Set Padding 20

Type "cwhelper setup" Enter
Sleep 1.5s
Type "https://your-org.atlassian.net" Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "jdoe@company.com" Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "your-api-token-here" Enter
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "y" Enter
Sleep 2s
